      <title>德国警告俄罗斯网络攻击行为将造成严重后果</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/germany-warns-consequences-alleged-russian-cyber-attack-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国外交部长安娜莱娜·贝尔博克 (Annalena Baerbock) 周五表示，俄罗斯将面临据称由与其军事情报部门有联系的组织策划的网络攻击的后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/germany-warns-consequences-alleged-russian-cyber-attack-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 04:06:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度曼尼普尔邦种族冲突周年纪念日高度戒备</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/high-security-indias-manipur-anniversary-ethnic-clashes-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，在印度陷入困境的东北部曼尼普尔邦，安全部队处于高度戒备状态，这是占多数的梅泰社区和库基部落之间爆发冲突一周年纪念日，这场冲突已造成至少 220 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/high-security-indias-manipur-anniversary-ethnic-clashes-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:39:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国将对食品供应商处以“收缩通货膨胀”罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/south-korea-slap-fines-food-suppliers-shrinkflation-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国反垄断监管机构周五表示，食品制造商和供应商如果减少产品尺寸，必须通知购物者，否则将面临最高 1000 万韩元（7,300 美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/south-korea-slap-fines-food-suppliers-shrinkflation-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:34:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国防部长称，菲律宾在南海造成的损害是“不负责任的行为”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/damage-injury-philippines-south-china-sea-is-irresponsible-behaviour-says-us-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周四在联合新闻发布会上表示，菲律宾船员在南海受伤和菲律宾船只受损是“不负责任的行为，无视国际法”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/damage-injury-philippines-south-china-sea-is-irresponsible-behaviour-says-us-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:08:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银表示全球对冲基金追逐港股反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-global-hedge-funds-chase-hong-kong-stocks-rally-ubs-says-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团在一份报告中表示，采用股票多空策略的全球对冲基金越来越看好中国，其购买香港上市股票的大幅增加就证明了这一点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-global-hedge-funds-chase-hong-kong-stocks-rally-ubs-says-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:48:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因科技股上涨而上涨；日元扩大涨势以限制疯狂的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受苹果创纪录的 1100 亿美元股票回购计划提振科技股走势的影响，亚洲股市周五上涨，而日元则进一步脱离近 34 年来的低点，结束了因疑似受到东京干预而动荡的一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:19:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾称中国飞机越过中线，中国进行着陆演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-14-chinese-military-planes-crossed-straits-median-line-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾国防部周五表示，发现中国军机再次侵入敏感的台湾海峡，中国报道称其海军已使用登陆艇进行了战斗演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-14-chinese-military-planes-crossed-straits-median-line-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:07:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保持警惕：受地震影响的台湾地震预警应用程序需求激增</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/stay-alert-quake-warning-app-demand-surges-earthquake-rattled-taiwan-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾地震预警智能手机应用程序在过去一个月里发生了 1,300 多次余震，在台湾发生了 1,300 多次余震，人们迫切希望获得额外几秒钟的时间来躲避，因此需求量激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/stay-alert-quake-warning-app-demand-surges-earthquake-rattled-taiwan-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:03:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾干涸的大坝揭示了数百年历史的城镇，吸引着游客</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/parched-philippine-dam-reveals-centuries-old-town-luring-tourists-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾北部一座因干旱而干涸的水坝上出现了一座具有数百年历史的城镇废墟，为依赖水稻种植的地区的居民带来了罕见的奇观和额外的收入来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/parched-philippine-dam-reveals-centuries-old-town-luring-tourists-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:02:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥当局搜寻失踪的澳大利亚和美国游客</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/mexican-authorities-search-missing-australian-us-tourists-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥当局周四表示，他们正在海上和陆地上搜寻两名澳大利亚人和一名据报在该国暴力最严重的州之一下加利福尼亚州失踪的美国人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/mexican-authorities-search-missing-australian-us-tourists-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
